                  arc_data_r PROC
;;;1380   
;;;1381       static int arc_data_r(                        /* ARGUMENTS                                     */
000000  e92d5fff          PUSH     {r0-r12,lr}
;;;1382       int move,                                     /* either G_2 (cw arc) or G_3 (ccw arc)          */
;;;1383       double current_x,                             /* first coordinate of current point             */
;;;1384       double current_y,                             /* second coordinate of current point            */

;;;1386       double end_y,                                 /* second coordinate of arc end point            */

;;;1389       double * center_y,                            /* pointer to second coordinate of center of arc */

                  convert_arc PROC
;;;1867   
;;;1868       static int convert_arc(                       /* ARGUMENTS                                */
000000  e92d4ff0          PUSH     {r4-r11,lr}
;;;1869       int move,                                     /* either G_2 (cw arc) or G_3 (ccw arc)     */
;;;1870       block_pointer block,                          /* pointer to a block of RS274 instructions */
;;;1871       setup_pointer settings)                       /* pointer to machine settings              */
;;;1872       {
000004  b093              SUB      sp,sp,#0x4c
000006  4682              MOV      r10,r0
000008  460c              MOV      r4,r1
00000a  4615              MOV      r5,r2
;;;1873           static char name[] SET_TO "convert_arc";
;;;1874           int status;
;;;1875           int first;                                /* flag set ON if this is first move after comp ON */
;;;1876           int ijk_flag;                             /* flag set ON if any of i,j,k present in NC code  */

;;;1878           double end_y;
;;;1879           double end_z;

;;;1881           double AA_end;                            /*AA*/
;;;1882   #endif
;;;1883   #ifdef BB
;;;1884           double BB_end;                            /*BB*/
;;;1885   #endif
;;;1886   #ifdef CC
;;;1887           double CC_end;                            /*CC*/
;;;1888   #endif
;;;1889   
;;;1890           ijk_flag SET_TO
00000c  f8d4014c          LDR      r0,[r4,#0x14c]
000010  b928              CBNZ     r0,|L10.30|
;;;1891               ((block->i_flag OR block->j_flag) OR block->k_flag) ? ON : OFF;

00001c  b110              CBZ      r0,|L10.36|
                  |L10.30|

000022  e001              B        |L10.40|
                  |L10.36|
000024  f04f0000          MOV      r0,#0
                  |L10.40|

;;;1892           first SET_TO (settings->program_x IS UNKNOWN);
00002a  f5054130          ADD      r1,r5,#0xb000
00002e  f50171bc          ADD      r1,r1,#0x178
000032  c903              LDM      r1,{r0,r1}
000034  4606              MOV      r6,r0
000036  4afb              LDR      r2,|L10.1060|
000038  4bfb              LDR      r3,|L10.1064|

                  |L10.70|

                  |L10.74|

;;;1893   
;;;1894           CHK(((block->r_flag ISNT ON) AND (ijk_flag ISNT ON)),

000072  4602              MOV      r2,r0

00007c  f6a06254          SUB      r2,r0,#0xe54
000080  eb021101          ADD      r1,r2,r1,LSL #4

                  |L10.166|
;;;1895               NCE_R_I_J_K_WORDS_ALL_MISSING_FOR_ARC);
;;;1896           CHK(((block->r_flag IS ON) AND (ijk_flag IS ON)),
;;;1897               NCE_MIXED_RADIUS_IJK_FORMAT_FOR_ARC);
;;;1898           if (settings->feed_mode IS UNITS_PER_MINUTE)
;;;1899           {
;;;1900               CHK((settings->feed_rate IS 0.0),
;;;1901                   NCE_CANNOT_MAKE_ARC_WITH_ZERO_FEED_RATE);
;;;1902           }
;;;1903           else if (settings->feed_mode IS INVERSE_TIME)
;;;1904           {
;;;1905               CHK((block->f_number IS -1.0),
;;;1906                   NCE_F_WORD_MISSING_WITH_INVERSE_TIME_ARC_MOVE);
;;;1907           }
;;;1908           if (ijk_flag)
;;;1909           {
;;;1910               if (settings->plane IS CANON_PLANE_XY)
;;;1911               {
;;;1912                   CHK((block->k_flag), NCE_K_WORD_GIVEN_FOR_ARC_IN_XY_PLANE);
;;;1913                   if (block->i_flag IS OFF)         /* i or j flag on to get here */
;;;1914                       block->i_number SET_TO 0.0;
;;;1915                   else if (block->j_flag IS OFF)
;;;1916                       block->j_number SET_TO 0.0;
;;;1917               }
;;;1918               else if (settings->plane IS CANON_PLANE_YZ)
;;;1919               {
;;;1920                   CHK((block->i_flag), NCE_I_WORD_GIVEN_FOR_ARC_IN_YZ_PLANE);
;;;1921                   if (block->j_flag IS OFF)         /* j or k flag on to get here */
;;;1922                       block->j_number SET_TO 0.0;
;;;1923                   else if (block->k_flag IS OFF)
;;;1924                       block->k_number SET_TO 0.0;
;;;1925               }
;;;1926               else if (settings->plane IS CANON_PLANE_XZ)
;;;1927               {
;;;1928                   CHK((block->j_flag), NCE_J_WORD_GIVEN_FOR_ARC_IN_XZ_PLANE);
;;;1929                   if (block->i_flag IS OFF)         /* i or k flag on to get here */
;;;1930                       block->i_number SET_TO 0.0;
;;;1931                   else if (block->k_flag IS OFF)
;;;1932                       block->k_number SET_TO 0.0;
;;;1933               }
;;;1934               else
;;;1935                   ERM(NCE_BUG_PLANE_NOT_XY_YZ_OR_XZ);
;;;1936           }
;;;1937           else;                                     /* r format arc; no other checks needed specific to this format */
;;;1938   
;;;1939           if (settings->plane IS CANON_PLANE_XY)    /* checks for both formats */
;;;1940            {
;;;1941               CHK(((block->x_flag IS OFF) AND (block->y_flag IS OFF)),
;;;1942                   NCE_X_AND_Y_WORDS_MISSING_FOR_ARC_IN_XY_PLANE);
;;;1943           }
;;;1944           else if (settings->plane IS CANON_PLANE_YZ)
;;;1945           {
;;;1946               CHK(((block->y_flag IS OFF) AND (block->z_flag IS OFF)),
;;;1947                   NCE_Y_AND_Z_WORDS_MISSING_FOR_ARC_IN_YZ_PLANE);
;;;1948           }
;;;1949           else if (settings->plane IS CANON_PLANE_XZ)
;;;1950           {
;;;1951               CHK(((block->x_flag IS OFF) AND (block->z_flag IS OFF)),
;;;1952                   NCE_X_AND_Z_WORDS_MISSING_FOR_ARC_IN_XZ_PLANE);
;;;1953           }
;;;1954   
;;;1955           find_ends(block, settings, &end_x, &end_y,
;;;1956               &end_z
;;;1957       #ifdef AA
;;;1958               , &AA_end
;;;1959       #endif
;;;1960   
;;;1961       #ifdef BB
;;;1962               , &BB_end
;;;1963       #endif
;;;1964   
;;;1965       #ifdef CC
;;;1966               , &CC_end
;;;1967       #endif
;;;1968               );
;;;1969           settings->motion_mode SET_TO move;
;;;1970   
;;;1971           if (settings->plane IS CANON_PLANE_XY)

                          AREA ||i.convert_arc_comp2||, CODE, READONLY, ALIGN=2

                  convert_arc_comp2 PROC
;;;2365   
;;;2366       static int convert_arc_comp2(                 /* ARGUMENTS                                 */
000000  e92d4fff          PUSH     {r0-r11,lr}
;;;2367       int move,                                     /* either G_2 (cw arc) or G_3 (ccw arc)           */
;;;2368       block_pointer block,                          /* pointer to a block of RS274/NGC instructions   */
;;;2369       setup_pointer settings,                       /* pointer to machine settings                    */
;;;2370       double end_x,                                 /* x-value at end of programmed (then actual) arc */
;;;2371       double end_y,                                 /* y-value at end of programmed (then actual) arc */
;;;2372       double end_z                                  /* z-value at end of arc                          */
;;;2373   #ifdef AA
;;;2374       , double AA_end                               /* a-value at end of arc                    *//*AA*/
;;;2375   #endif
;;;2376   #ifdef BB
;;;2377       , double BB_end                               /* b-value at end of arc                    *//*BB*/
;;;2378   #endif
;;;2379   #ifdef CC
;;;2380       , double CC_end                               /* c-value at end of arc                    *//*CC*/
;;;2381   #endif
;;;2382       )
;;;2383       {
000004  b0b7              SUB      sp,sp,#0xdc
000006  4616              MOV      r6,r2
000008  ac44              ADD      r4,sp,#0x110
00000a  e89407b0          LDM      r4,{r4,r5,r7-r10}
;;;2384           static char name[] SET_TO "convert_arc_comp2";
;;;2385           double alpha;                             /* direction of tangent to start of arc */
;;;2386           double arc_radius;
;;;2387           double beta;                              /* angle between two tangents above */
;;;2388           double center_x;                          /* center of arc */
;;;2389           double center_y;
;;;2390           double delta;                             /* direction of radius from start of arc to center of arc */
;;;2391           double gamma;                             /* direction of perpendicular to arc at end */
;;;2392           double mid_x;
;;;2393           double mid_y;
;;;2394           int side;
;;;2395      /* angle for testing corners */
;;;2396           double small SET_TO TOLERANCE_CONCAVE_CORNER;
00000e  49ff              LDR      r1,|L13.1036|
000010  48ff              LDR      r0,|L13.1040|
000012  e9cd1022          STRD     r1,r0,[sp,#0x88]
;;;2397           double start_x;
;;;2398           double start_y;
;;;2399           int status;                               /* status returned from CHP function call     */
;;;2400           double theta;                             /* direction of tangent to last cut */
;;;2401           double tolerance;
;;;2402           double tool_radius;
;;;2403           int turn;                                 /* number of full or partial circles CCW */
;;;2404   
;;;2405      /* find basic arc data: center_x, center_y, and turn */
;;;2406   
;;;2407           start_x SET_TO settings->program_x;
000016  f5064130          ADD      r1,r6,#0xb000
00001a  f50171bc          ADD      r1,r1,#0x178
00001e  c903              LDM      r1,{r0,r1}
000020  e9cd0120          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x80]
;;;2408           start_y SET_TO settings->program_y;
000024  f5064030          ADD      r0,r6,#0xb000
000028  f50070c0          ADD      r0,r0,#0x180
00002c  c803              LDM      r0,{r0,r1}
00002e  e9cd011e          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x78]
;;;2409           tolerance SET_TO (settings->length_units IS CANON_UNITS_INCHES) ?
000032  f8d6051c          LDR      r0,[r6,#0x51c]
000036  2801              CMP      r0,#1

                          AREA ||i.convert_axis_offsets||, CODE, READONLY, ALIGN=2

                  convert_axis_offsets PROC
;;;2625   
;;;2626       static int convert_axis_offsets(              /* ARGUMENTS                               */
000000  e92d4ff0          PUSH     {r4-r11,lr}
;;;2627       int g_code,                                   /* g_code being executed (must be in G_92 series) */
;;;2628       block_pointer block,                          /* pointer to a block of RS274/NGC instructions   */
;;;2629       setup_pointer settings)                       /* pointer to machine settings                    */
;;;2630       {
000004  b089              SUB      sp,sp,#0x24
000006  4681              MOV      r9,r0
000008  4688              MOV      r8,r1
00000a  4614              MOV      r4,r2
;;;2631           static char name[] SET_TO "convert_axis_offsets";
;;;2632           double * pars;                            /* short name for settings->parameters            */
;;;2633   
;;;2634           CHK((settings->cutter_comp_side ISNT OFF),/* not "IS ON" */
00000c  f8d403b0          LDR      r0,[r4,#0x3b0]
000010  b340              CBZ      r0,|L14.100|

000018  f8c0114c          STR      r1,[r0,#0x14c]
00001c  4601              MOV      r1,r0
00001e  f8d1314c          LDR      r3,[r1,#0x14c]

00002a  4602              MOV      r2,r0

000034  f6a06254          SUB      r2,r0,#0xe54

000048  48f2              LDR      r0,|L14.1044|
00004a  f8d0014c          LDR      r0,[r0,#0x14c]

000058  7001              STRB     r1,[r0,#0]
00005a  f04f0026          MOV      r0,#0x26
                  |L14.94|
;;;2635               NCE_CANNOT_CHANGE_AXIS_OFFSETS_WITH_CUTTER_RADIUS_COMP);
;;;2636           pars SET_TO settings->parameters;
;;;2637           if (g_code IS G_92)
;;;2638           {
;;;2639               if (block->x_flag IS ON)
;;;2640               {
;;;2641                   settings->axis_offset_x SET_TO
;;;2642                       (settings->current_x + settings->axis_offset_x - block->x_number);
;;;2643                   settings->current_x SET_TO block->x_number;
;;;2644               }
;;;2645   
;;;2646               if (block->y_flag IS ON)
;;;2647               {
;;;2648                   settings->axis_offset_y SET_TO
;;;2649                       (settings->current_y + settings->axis_offset_y - block->y_number);
;;;2650                   settings->current_y SET_TO block->y_number;
;;;2651               }
;;;2652   
;;;2653               if (block->z_flag IS ON)
;;;2654               {
;;;2655                   settings->axis_offset_z SET_TO
;;;2656                       (settings->current_z + settings->axis_offset_z - block->z_number);
;;;2657                   settings->current_z SET_TO block->z_number;
;;;2658               }
;;;2659   
;;;2660   #ifdef AA
;;;2661               if (block->a_flag IS ON)              /*AA*/
;;;2662   #endif
;;;2663   #ifdef AA
;;;2664               {                                     /*AA*/
;;;2665                   settings->AA_axis_offset SET_TO (settings->AA_current +
;;;2666       #endif
;;;2667       #ifdef AA
;;;2668      /*AA*/
;;;2669                       settings->AA_axis_offset - block->a_number);
;;;2670   #endif
;;;2671   #ifdef AA
;;;2672      /*AA*/
;;;2673                   settings->AA_current SET_TO block->a_number;
;;;2674               }
;;;2675   #endif
;;;2676   
;;;2677   #ifdef BB
;;;2678               if (block->b_flag IS ON)              /*BB*/
;;;2679   #endif
;;;2680   #ifdef BB
;;;2681               {                                     /*BB*/
;;;2682                   settings->BB_axis_offset SET_TO (settings->BB_current +
;;;2683       #endif
;;;2684       #ifdef BB
;;;2685      /*BB*/
;;;2686                       settings->BB_axis_offset - block->b_number);
;;;2687   #endif
;;;2688   #ifdef BB
;;;2689      /*BB*/
;;;2690                   settings->BB_current SET_TO block->b_number;
;;;2691               }
;;;2692   #endif
;;;2693

                  convert_cycle_g81 PROC
;;;3531   
;;;3532       static int convert_cycle_g81(                 /* ARGUMENTS                        */
000000  e92d5fff          PUSH     {r0-r12,lr}
;;;3533       CANON_PLANE plane,                            /* selected plane                   */
;;;3534       double x,                                     /* x-value where cycle is executed  */
;;;3535       double y,                                     /* y-value where cycle is executed  */
;;;3536       double clear_z,                               /* z-value of clearance plane       */
;;;3537       double bottom_z)                              /* value of z at bottom of cycle    */
;;;3538       {

000006  4616              MOV      r6,r2
000008  461f              MOV      r7,r3
00000a  ac12              ADD      r4,sp,#0x48
00000c  e8940f30          LDM      r4,{r4,r5,r8-r11}
;;;3539   //        static char name[] SET_TO "convert_cycle_g81";
;;;3540   
;;;3541           cycle_feed(plane, x, y, bottom_z);

000012  463b              MOV      r3,r7

000018  9804              LDR      r0,[sp,#0x10]

;;;3542           cycle_traverse(plane, x, y, clear_z);

000020  463b              MOV      r3,r7
000022  e88d0330          STM      sp,{r4,r5,r8,r9}
000026  9804              LDR      r0,[sp,#0x10]
000028  f7fffffe          BL       cycle_traverse
;;;3543   
;;;3544           return RS274NGC_OK;
00002c  2000              MOVS     r0,#0
;;;3545       }
00002e  b008              ADD      sp,sp,#0x20
000030  e8bd9ff0          POP      {r4-r12,pc}
;;;3546   
                          ENDP

;;;3624

                  convert_cycle_g89 PROC
;;;3994   
;;;3995       static int convert_cycle_g89(                 /* ARGUMENTS                        */
000000  e92d5fff          PUSH     {r0-r12,lr}
;;;3996       CANON_PLANE plane,                            /* selected plane                   */
;;;3997       double x,                                     /* x-value where cycle is executed  */
;;;3998       double y,                                     /* y-value where cycle is executed  */
;;;3999       double clear_z,                               /* z-value of clearance plane       */
;;;4000       double bottom_z,                              /* value of z at bottom of cycle    */
;;;4001       double dwell)                                 /* dwell time                       */
;;;4002       {
000004  b084              SUB      sp,sp,#0x10
000006  4616              MOV      r6,r2
000008  461f              MOV      r7,r3
00000a  ac12              ADD      r4,sp,#0x48
00000c  e8940f30          LDM      r4,{r4,r5,r8-r11}
;;;4003   //        static char name[] SET_TO "convert_cycle_g89";
;;;4004   
;;;4005           cycle_feed(plane, x, y, bottom_z);
000010  4632              MOV      r2,r6
000012  463b              MOV      r3,r7
000014  e88d0c30          STM      sp,{r4,r5,r10,r11}
000018  9804              LDR      r0,[sp,#0x10]
00001a  f7fffffe          BL       cycle_feed
;;;4006           DWELL(dwell);
00001e  e9dd0118          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x60]
000022  f7fffffe          BL       DWELL
;;;4007           cycle_feed(plane, x, y, clear_z);
000026  4632              MOV      r2,r6
000028  463b              MOV      r3,r7
00002a  e88d0330          STM      sp,{r4,r5,r8,r9}
00002e  9804              LDR      r0,[sp,#0x10]
000030  f7fffffe          BL       cycle_feed
;;;4008   
;;;4009           return RS274NGC_OK;
000034  2000              MOVS     r0,#0
;;;4010       }
000036  b008              ADD      sp,sp,#0x20
000038  e8bd9ff0          POP      {r4-r12,pc}
;;;4011   
                          ENDP

                  convert_cycle_xy PROC
;;;4128   
;;;4129           static int convert_cycle_xy(              /* ARGUMENTS                                 */

000064  f04f00c3          MOV      r0,#0xc3
                  |L31.104|
;;;4155                   NCE_Z_VALUE_UNSPECIFIED_IN_XY_PLANE_CANNED_CYCLE);
;;;4156           }
;;;4157           block->z_number SET_TO
;;;4158               block->z_flag IS ON ? block->z_number : settings->cycle_cc;
;;;4159           old_cc SET_TO settings->current_z;
;;;4160   
;;;4161           if (settings->distance_mode IS MODE_ABSOLUTE)
;;;4162           {
;;;4163               aa_increment SET_TO 0.0;
;;;4164               bb_increment SET_TO 0.0;
;;;4165               r SET_TO block->r_number;
;;;4166               cc SET_TO block->z_number;
;;;4167               aa SET_TO block->x_flag IS ON ? block->x_number : settings->current_x;
;;;4168               bb SET_TO block->y_flag IS ON ? block->y_number : settings->current_y;
;;;4169           }
;;;4170           else if (settings->distance_mode IS MODE_INCREMENTAL)
;;;4171           {
;;;4172               aa_increment SET_TO block->x_number;
;;;4173               bb_increment SET_TO block->y_number;
;;;4174               r SET_TO (block->r_number + old_cc);
;;;4175               cc SET_TO (r + block->z_number);      /* [NCMS, page 98] */
;;;4176               aa SET_TO settings->current_x;
;;;4177               bb SET_TO settings->current_y;
;;;4178           }
;;;4179           else
;;;4180               ERM(NCE_BUG_DISTANCE_MODE_NOT_G90_OR_G91);
;;;4181           CHK((r < cc), NCE_R_LESS_THAN_Z_IN_CYCLE_IN_XY_PLANE);
;;;4182   
;;;4183           if (old_cc < r)
;;;4184           {
;;;4185               STRAIGHT_TRAVERSE(settings->current_x, settings->current_y, r
;;;4186       #ifdef AA
;;;4187                   ,     settings->AA_current
;;;4188       #else
;;;4189       #ifdef ALL_AXES
;;;4190                   , 0
;;;4191       #endif
;;;4192       #endif
;;;4193       #ifdef BB
;;;4194                   ,  settings->BB_current
;;;4195       #else
;;;4196       #ifdef ALL_AXES
;;;4197                   , 0
;;;4198       #endif
;;;4199       #endif

;;;4202       #else
;;;4203       #ifdef ALL_AXES
;;;4204                   , 0
;;;4205       #endif
;;;4206       #endif

;;;4208               old_cc SET_TO r;
;;;4209           }
;;;4210           clear_cc SET_TO (settings->retract_mode IS R_PLANE) ? r : old_cc;
;;;4211   
;;;4212           save_mode SET_TO GET_EXTERNAL_MOTION_CONTROL_MODE();
;;;4213           if (save_mode ISNT CANON_EXACT_PATH)
;;;4214               SET_MOTION_CONTROL_MODE(CANON_EXACT_PATH);
;;;4215   
;;;4216           switch(motion)
;;;4217           {
;;;4218               case G_81:
;;;4219                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g81(CANON_PLANE_XY, aa, bb, clear_cc, cc))

;;;4221               case G_82:

;;;4225                       block->p_number IS -1.0 ? settings->cycle_p : block->p_number;

;;;4227                       block->p_number))
;;;4228                       settings->cycle_p SET_TO block->p_number;
;;;4229                   break;

;;;4232                       NCE_Q_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G83);

;;;4234                       block->q_number IS -1.0 ? settings->cycle_q : block->q_number;
;;;4235                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g83 (CANON_PLANE_XY, aa, bb, r, clear_cc, cc,
;;;4236                       block->q_number))
;;;4237                       settings->cycle_q SET_TO block->q_number;
;;;4238                   break;
;;;4239               case G_84:
;;;4240                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g84 (CANON_PLANE_XY, aa, bb, clear_cc, cc,
;;;4241                       settings->spindle_turning, settings->speed_feed_mode))
;;;4242                       break;
;;;4243               case G_85:
;;;4244                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g85 (CANON_PLANE_XY, aa, bb, clear_cc, cc))
;;;4245                       break;
;;;4246               case G_86:
;;;4247                   CHK(((settings->motion_mode ISNT G_86) AND (block->p_number IS -1.0)),
;;;4248                       NCE_DWELL_TIME_P_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G86);
;;;4249                   block->p_number SET_TO
;;;4250                       block->p_number IS -1.0 ? settings->cycle_p : block->p_number;
;;;4251                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g86 (CANON_PLANE_XY, aa, bb, clear_cc, cc,
;;;4252                       block->p_number, settings->spindle_turning))
;;;4253                       settings->cycle_p SET_TO block->p_number;
;;;4254                   break;
;;;4255               case G_87:
;;;4256                   if (settings->motion_mode ISNT G_87)
;;;4257                   {
;;;4258                       CHK((block->i_flag IS OFF), NCE_I_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G87);

;;;4268                   if (settings->distance_mode IS MODE_INCREMENTAL)
;;;4269                   {
;;;4270                       k SET_TO (cc + k);            /* k always absolute in function call below */
;;;4271                   }
;;;4272                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g87 (CANON_PLANE_XY, aa, (aa + i), bb,
;;;4273                       (bb + j), r, clear_cc, k, cc, settings->spindle_turning))
;;;4274                       break;
;;;4275               case G_88:
;;;4276                   CHK(((settings->motion_mode ISNT G_88) AND (block->p_number IS -1.0)),
;;;4277                       NCE_DWELL_TIME_P_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G88);

;;;4282                       settings->cycle_p SET_TO block->p_number;
;;;4283                   break;
;;;4284               case G_89:

;;;4287                   block->p_number SET_TO
;;;4288                       block->p_number IS -1.0 ? settings->cycle_p : block->p_number;

;;;4291                       settings->cycle_p SET_TO block->p_number;
;;;4292                   break;
;;;4293               default:

;;;4296           settings->current_x SET_TO aa;            /* CYCLE_MACRO updates aa and bb */

                  convert_cycle_yz PROC
;;;4355   
;;;4356       static int convert_cycle_yz(                  /* ARGUMENTS                                 */

;;;4385               block->x_flag IS ON ? block->x_number : settings->cycle_cc;
;;;4386           old_cc SET_TO settings->current_x;
;;;4387   
;;;4388           if (settings->distance_mode IS MODE_ABSOLUTE)
;;;4389           {
;;;4390               aa_increment SET_TO 0.0;
;;;4391               bb_increment SET_TO 0.0;

;;;4400               bb_increment SET_TO block->z_number;

;;;4404               bb SET_TO settings->current_z;
;;;4405           }
;;;4406           else

;;;4408           CHK((r < cc), NCE_R_LESS_THAN_X_IN_CYCLE_IN_YZ_PLANE);
;;;4409   
;;;4410           if (old_cc < r)
;;;4411           {
;;;4412               STRAIGHT_TRAVERSE(r, settings->current_y, settings->current_z
;;;4413       #ifdef AA

;;;4418       #endif

;;;4425       #endif
;;;4426       #endif

;;;4429       #else
;;;4430       #ifdef ALL_AXES

;;;4432       #endif
;;;4433       #endif

;;;4435               old_cc SET_TO r;
;;;4436           }

;;;4439           save_mode = GET_EXTERNAL_MOTION_CONTROL_MODE();

;;;4442   
;;;4443           switch(motion)
;;;4444           {
;;;4445               case G_81:
;;;4446                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g81(CANON_PLANE_YZ, aa, bb, clear_cc, cc))
;;;4447                       break;
;;;4448               case G_82:

;;;4450                       NCE_DWELL_TIME_P_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G82);

;;;4452                       block->p_number IS -1.0 ? settings->cycle_p : block->p_number;

;;;4455                       settings->cycle_p SET_TO block->p_number;

;;;4464                       settings->cycle_q SET_TO block->q_number;
;;;4465                   break;

;;;4467                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g84 (CANON_PLANE_YZ, aa, bb, clear_cc, cc,
;;;4468                       settings->spindle_turning, settings->speed_feed_mode))
;;;4469                       break;
;;;4470               case G_85:
;;;4471                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g85 (CANON_PLANE_YZ, aa, bb, clear_cc, cc))
;;;4472                       break;
;;;4473               case G_86:
;;;4474                   CHK(((settings->motion_mode ISNT G_86) AND (block->p_number IS -1.0)),
;;;4475                       NCE_DWELL_TIME_P_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G86);
;;;4476                   block->p_number SET_TO
;;;4477                       block->p_number IS -1.0 ? settings->cycle_p : block->p_number;
;;;4478                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g86 (CANON_PLANE_YZ, aa, bb, clear_cc, cc,
;;;4479                       block->p_number, settings->spindle_turning))
;;;4480                       settings->cycle_p SET_TO block->p_number;
;;;4481                   break;
;;;4482               case G_87:
;;;4483                   if (settings->motion_mode ISNT G_87)
;;;4484                   {
;;;4485                       CHK((block->i_flag IS OFF), NCE_I_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G87);
;;;4486                       CHK((block->j_flag IS OFF), NCE_J_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G87);
;;;4487                       CHK((block->k_flag IS OFF), NCE_K_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G87);
;;;4488                   }
;;;4489                   i SET_TO block->i_flag IS ON ? block->i_number : settings->cycle_i;
;;;4490                   j SET_TO block->j_flag IS ON ? block->j_number : settings->cycle_j;
;;;4491                   k SET_TO block->k_flag IS ON ? block->k_number : settings->cycle_k;
;;;4492                   settings->cycle_i SET_TO i;
;;;4493                   settings->cycle_j SET_TO j;
;;;4494                   settings->cycle_k SET_TO k;
;;;4495                   if (settings->distance_mode IS MODE_INCREMENTAL)
;;;4496                   {
;;;4497                       i SET_TO (cc + i);            /* i always absolute in function call below */
;;;4498                   }
;;;4499                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g87 (CANON_PLANE_YZ, aa, (aa + j), bb,
;;;4500                       (bb + k), r, clear_cc, i, cc, settings->spindle_turning))
;;;4501                       break;
;;;4502               case G_88:
;;;4503                   CHK(((settings->motion_mode ISNT G_88) AND (block->p_number IS -1.0)),
;;;4504                       NCE_DWELL_TIME_P_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G88);
;;;4505                   block->p_number SET_TO
;;;4506                       block->p_number IS -1.0 ? settings->cycle_p : block->p_number;
;;;4507                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g88 (CANON_PLANE_YZ, aa, bb, cc,
;;;4508                       block->p_number, settings->spindle_turning))
;;;4509                       settings->cycle_p SET_TO block->p_number;
;;;4510                   break;
;;;4511               case G_89:
;;;4512                   CHK(((settings->motion_mode ISNT G_89) AND (block->p_number IS -1.0)),
;;;4513                       NCE_DWELL_TIME_P_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G89);
;;;4514                   block->p_number SET_TO
;;;4515                       block->p_number IS -1.0 ? settings->cycle_p : block->p_number;

;;;4518                       settings->cycle_p SET_TO block->p_number;
;;;4519                   break;
;;;4520               default:
;;;4521                   ERM(NCE_BUG_FUNCTION_SHOULD_NOT_HAVE_BEEN_CALLED);
;;;4522           }
;;;4523           settings->current_y SET_TO aa;            /* CYCLE_MACRO updates aa and bb */
;;;4524           settings->current_z SET_TO bb;
;;;4525           settings->current_x SET_TO clear_cc;
;;;4526           settings->cycle_cc SET_TO block->x_number;

;;;4529               SET_MOTION_CONTROL_MODE(save_mode);

;;;4532       }

                          AREA ||i.convert_cycle_zx||, CODE, READONLY, ALIGN=2

                  convert_cycle_zx PROC
;;;4590   
;;;4591       static int convert_cycle_zx(                  /* ARGUMENTS                                 */
000000  b507              PUSH     {r0-r2,lr}
;;;4592       int motion,                                   /* a g-code between G_81 and G_89, a canned cycle */
;;;4593       block_pointer block,                          /* pointer to a block of RS274 instructions       */
;;;4594       setup_pointer settings)                       /* pointer to machine settings                    */
;;;4595       {
000002  b0b0              SUB      sp,sp,#0xc0
;;;4596           static char name[] SET_TO "convert_cycle_zx";
;;;4597           double aa;
;;;4598           double aa_increment;
;;;4599           double bb;
;;;4600           double bb_increment;
;;;4601           double cc;
;;;4602           double clear_cc;
;;;4603           double i;
;;;4604           double j;
;;;4605           double k;
;;;4606           double old_cc;
;;;4607           CANON_PLANE plane;
;;;4608           double r;
;;;4609           int repeat;
;;;4610           CANON_MOTION_MODE save_mode;
;;;4611           int status;
;;;4612   
;;;4613           plane SET_TO CANON_PLANE_XZ;
000004  f04f0003          MOV      r0,#3
000008  901b              STR      r0,[sp,#0x6c]
;;;4614           if (settings->motion_mode ISNT motion)
00000a  9832              LDR      r0,[sp,#0xc8]
00000c  f8d01628          LDR      r1,[r0,#0x628]
000010  9830              LDR      r0,[sp,#0xc0]
000012  4281              CMP      r1,r0
000014  d02a              BEQ      |L33.108|
;;;4615           {
;;;4616               CHK((block->y_flag IS OFF),
000016  9831              LDR      r0,[sp,#0xc4]
000018  f8d001e8          LDR      r0,[r0,#0x1e8]
00001c  bb30              CBNZ     r0,|L33.108|
00001e  f04f0100          MOV      r1,#0
000022  48ff              LDR      r0,|L33.1056|
000024  f8c0114c          STR      r1,[r0,#0x14c]
000028  f8d0214c          LDR      r2,[r0,#0x14c]

000034  49fa              LDR      r1,|L33.1056|

000042  eb011000          ADD      r0,r1,r0,LSL #4
000046  49f7              LDR      r1,|L33.1060|

00005e  eb021000          ADD      r0,r2,r0,LSL #4
000062  7001              STRB     r1,[r0,#0]
000064  f04f00c2          MOV      r0,#0xc2
                  |L33.104|
;;;4617                   NCE_Y_VALUE_UNSPECIFIED_IN_XZ_PLANE_CANNED_CYCLE);
;;;4618           }
;;;4619           block->y_number SET_TO
;;;4620               block->y_flag IS ON ? block->y_number : settings->cycle_cc;
;;;4621           old_cc SET_TO settings->current_y;
;;;4622   
;;;4623           if (settings->distance_mode IS MODE_ABSOLUTE)
;;;4624           {
;;;4625               aa_increment SET_TO 0.0;
;;;4626               bb_increment SET_TO 0.0;
;;;4627               r SET_TO block->r_number;
;;;4628               cc SET_TO block->y_number;
;;;4629               aa SET_TO block->z_flag IS ON ? block->z_number : settings->current_z;
;;;4630               bb SET_TO block->x_flag IS ON ? block->x_number : settings->current_x;
;;;4631           }
;;;4632           else if (settings->distance_mode IS MODE_INCREMENTAL)
;;;4633           {
;;;4634               aa_increment SET_TO block->z_number;
;;;4635               bb_increment SET_TO block->x_number;
;;;4636               r SET_TO (block->r_number + old_cc);
;;;4637               cc SET_TO (r + block->y_number);      /* [NCMS, page 98] */
;;;4638               aa SET_TO settings->current_z;
;;;4639               bb SET_TO settings->current_x;
;;;4640           }
;;;4641           else
;;;4642               ERM(NCE_BUG_DISTANCE_MODE_NOT_G90_OR_G91);
;;;4643           CHK((r < cc), NCE_R_LESS_THAN_Y_IN_CYCLE_IN_XZ_PLANE);
;;;4644   
;;;4645           if (old_cc < r)
;;;4646           {
;;;4647               STRAIGHT_TRAVERSE(settings->current_x, r, settings->current_z
;;;4648       #ifdef AA
;;;4649                   ,           settings->AA_current
;;;4650       #else
;;;4651       #ifdef ALL_AXES
;;;4652                   , 0
;;;4653       #endif
;;;4654       #endif
;;;4655       #ifdef BB
;;;4656                   ,  settings->BB_current
;;;4657       #else
;;;4658       #ifdef ALL_AXES
;;;4659                   , 0
;;;4660       #endif
;;;4661       #endif
;;;4662       #ifdef CC
;;;4663                   ,  settings->CC_current
;;;4664       #else
;;;4665       #ifdef ALL_AXES
;;;4666                   , 0
;;;4667       #endif
;;;4668       #endif
;;;4669                   );
;;;4670               old_cc SET_TO r;
;;;4671           }
;;;4672           clear_cc SET_TO (settings->retract_mode IS R_PLANE) ? r : old_cc;
;;;4673   
;;;4674           save_mode = GET_EXTERNAL_MOTION_CONTROL_MODE();
;;;4675           if (save_mode ISNT CANON_EXACT_PATH)
;;;4676               SET_MOTION_CONTROL_MODE(CANON_EXACT_PATH);
;;;4677   
;;;4678           switch(motion)
;;;4679           {
;;;4680               case G_81:
;;;4681                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g81(CANON_PLANE_XZ, aa, bb, clear_cc, cc))
;;;4682                       break;
;;;4683               case G_82:
;;;4684                   CHK(((settings->motion_mode ISNT G_82) AND (block->p_number IS -1.0)),
;;;4685                       NCE_DWELL_TIME_P_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G82);
;;;4686                   block->p_number SET_TO
;;;4687                       block->p_number IS -1.0 ? settings->cycle_p : block->p_number;
;;;4688                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g82 (CANON_PLANE_XZ, aa, bb, clear_cc, cc,
;;;4689                       block->p_number))
;;;4690                       settings->cycle_p SET_TO block->p_number;
;;;4691                   break;
;;;4692               case G_83:
;;;4693                   CHK(((settings->motion_mode ISNT G_83) AND (block->q_number IS -1.0)),
;;;4694                       NCE_Q_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G83);
;;;4695                   block->q_number SET_TO
;;;4696                       block->q_number IS -1.0 ? settings->cycle_q : block->q_number;
;;;4697                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g83 (CANON_PLANE_XZ, aa, bb, r, clear_cc, cc,
;;;4698                       block->q_number))
;;;4699                       settings->cycle_q SET_TO block->q_number;
;;;4700                   break;
;;;4701               case G_84:
;;;4702                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g84 (CANON_PLANE_XZ, aa, bb, clear_cc, cc,
;;;4703                       settings->spindle_turning, settings->speed_feed_mode))
;;;4704                       break;
;;;4705               case G_85:
;;;4706                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g85 (CANON_PLANE_XZ, aa, bb, clear_cc, cc))
;;;4707                       break;
;;;4708               case G_86:
;;;4709                   CHK(((settings->motion_mode ISNT G_86) AND (block->p_number IS -1.0)),
;;;4710                       NCE_DWELL_TIME_P_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G86);
;;;4711                   block->p_number SET_TO
;;;4712                       block->p_number IS -1.0 ? settings->cycle_p : block->p_number;
;;;4713                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g86 (CANON_PLANE_XZ, aa, bb, clear_cc, cc,
;;;4714                       block->p_number, settings->spindle_turning))
;;;4715                       settings->cycle_p SET_TO block->p_number;
;;;4716                   break;
;;;4717               case G_87:
;;;4718                   if (settings->motion_mode ISNT G_87)
;;;4719                   {
;;;4720                       CHK((block->i_flag IS OFF), NCE_I_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G87);
;;;4721                       CHK((block->j_flag IS OFF), NCE_J_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G87);
;;;4722                       CHK((block->k_flag IS OFF), NCE_K_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G87);
;;;4723                   }
;;;4724                   i SET_TO block->i_flag IS ON ? block->i_number : settings->cycle_i;
;;;4725                   j SET_TO block->j_flag IS ON ? block->j_number : settings->cycle_j;
;;;4726                   k SET_TO block->k_flag IS ON ? block->k_number : settings->cycle_k;
;;;4727                   settings->cycle_i SET_TO i;
;;;4728                   settings->cycle_j SET_TO j;
;;;4729                   settings->cycle_k SET_TO k;
;;;4730                   if (settings->distance_mode IS MODE_INCREMENTAL)
;;;4731                   {
;;;4732                       j SET_TO (cc + j);            /* j always absolute in function call below */
;;;4733                   }
;;;4734                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g87 (CANON_PLANE_XZ, aa, (aa + k), bb,
;;;4735                       (bb + i), r, clear_cc, j, cc, settings->spindle_turning))
;;;4736                       break;
;;;4737               case G_88:
;;;4738                   CHK(((settings->motion_mode ISNT G_88) AND (block->p_number IS -1.0)),
;;;4739                       NCE_DWELL_TIME_P_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G88);
;;;4740                   block->p_number SET_TO
;;;4741                       block->p_number IS -1.0 ? settings->cycle_p : block->p_number;
;;;4742                   CYCLE_MACRO(convert_cycle_g88 (CANON_PLANE_XZ, aa, bb, cc,
;;;4743                       block->p_number, settings->spindle_turning))
;;;4744                       settings->cycle_p SET_TO block->p_number;
;;;4745                   break;
;;;4746               case G_89:
;;;4747                   CHK(((settings->motion_mode ISNT G_89) AND (block->p_number IS -1.0)),
;;;4748                       NCE_DWELL_TIME_P_WORD_MISSING_WITH_G89);

;;;4869

                  convert_setup PROC
;;;5687   	
;;;5688       static int convert_setup(                     /* ARGUMENTS                                    */
000000  e92d4ff0          PUSH     {r4-r11,lr}
;;;5689       block_pointer block,                          /* pointer to a block of RS274/NGC instructions */
;;;5690       setup_pointer settings)                       /* pointer to machine settings                  */
;;;5691       {
000004  b08b              SUB      sp,sp,#0x2c
000006  4683              MOV      r11,r0
000008  468a              MOV      r10,r1
;;;5692   //        static char name[] SET_TO "convert_setup";
;;;5693           double x;
;;;5694           double y;
;;;5695           double z;
;;;5696   #ifdef AA
;;;5697           double a;                                 /*AA*/
;;;5698   #endif
;;;5699   #ifdef BB
;;;5700           double b;                                 /*BB*/
;;;5701   #endif
;;;5702   #ifdef CC
;;;5703           double c;                                 /*CC*/
;;;5704   #endif
;;;5705           double * parameters;
;;;5706           int p_int;
;;;5707   
;;;5708           parameters SET_TO settings->parameters;
00000a  f50a60c9          ADD      r0,r10,#0x648
00000e  9009              STR      r0,[sp,#0x24]
;;;5709           p_int SET_TO (int)(block->p_number + 0.0001);
000010  f50b70d8          ADD      r0,r11,#0x1b0
000014  c803              LDM      r0,{r0,r1}
000016  4a7f              LDR      r2,|L46.532|
000018  4b7f              LDR      r3,|L46.536|
00001a  e9cd0104          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x10]
00001e  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dadd
000022  e9cd0106          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x18]
000026  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_d2iz
00002a  9008              STR      r0,[sp,#0x20]
;;;5710   
;;;5711           if (block->x_flag IS ON)
00002c  f8db01dc          LDR      r0,[r11,#0x1dc]
000030  2801              CMP      r0,#1
000032  d10e              BNE      |L46.82|
;;;5712           {
;;;5713               x SET_TO block->x_number;
000034  f50b74f0          ADD      r4,r11,#0x1e0
000038  cc30              LDM      r4,{r4,r5}
;;;5714               parameters[5201 + (p_int * 20)] SET_TO x;
00003a  9808              LDR      r0,[sp,#0x20]
00003c  eb000080          ADD      r0,r0,r0,LSL #2
000040  f2414151          MOV      r1,#0x1451
000044  eb010180          ADD      r1,r1,r0,LSL #2
000048  9809              LDR      r0,[sp,#0x24]
00004a  eb0000c1          ADD      r0,r0,r1,LSL #3
00004e  c030              STM      r0!,{r4,r5}
000050  e00a              B        |L46.104|
                  |L46.82|
;;;5715           }
;;;5716           else
;;;5717               x SET_TO parameters[5201 + (p_int * 20)];
000052  9808              LDR      r0,[sp,#0x20]
000054  eb000080          ADD      r0,r0,r0,LSL #2
000058  f2414151          MOV      r1,#0x1451
00005c  eb010180          ADD      r1,r1,r0,LSL #2
000060  9809              LDR      r0,[sp,#0x24]
000062  eb0000c1          ADD      r0,r0,r1,LSL #3
000066  c830              LDM      r0!,{r4,r5}
                  |L46.104|
;;;5718   
;;;5719           if (block->y_flag IS ON)
000068  f8db01e8          LDR      r0,[r11,#0x1e8]
00006c  2801              CMP      r0,#1
00006e  d10e              BNE      |L46.142|
;;;5720           {
;;;5721               y SET_TO block->y_number;
000070  f50b76f8          ADD      r6,r11,#0x1f0
000074  cec0              LDM      r6,{r6,r7}
;;;5722               parameters[5202 + (p_int * 20)] SET_TO y;
000076  9808              LDR      r0,[sp,#0x20]
000078  eb000080          ADD      r0,r0,r0,LSL #2
00007c  f2414152          MOV      r1,#0x1452
000080  eb010180          ADD      r1,r1,r0,LSL #2
000084  9809              LDR      r0,[sp,#0x24]

00008c  e00a              B        |L46.164|
                  |L46.142|
;;;5723           }
;;;5724           else
;;;5725               y SET_TO parameters[5202 + (p_int * 20)];
00008e  9808              LDR      r0,[sp,#0x20]
000090  eb000080          ADD      r0,r0,r0,LSL #2

                  |L46.164|
;;;5726           if (block->z_flag IS ON)

;;;5727           {

;;;5729               parameters[5203 + (p_int * 20)] SET_TO z;

;;;5730           }
;;;5731           else
;;;5732               z SET_TO parameters[5203 + (p_int * 20)];

0000e2  e9d08900          LDRD     r8,r9,[r0,#0]
                  |L46.230|
;;;5733   
;;;5734   #ifdef AA
;;;5735           if (block->a_flag IS ON)
;;;5736           {
;;;5737               a SET_TO block->a_number;
;;;5738               parameters[5204 + (p_int * 20)] SET_TO a;
;;;5739           }
;;;5740           else
;;;5741               a SET_TO parameters[5204 + (p_int * 20)];
;;;5742   #endif
;;;5743   
;;;5744   #ifdef BB
;;;5745           if (block->b_flag IS ON)
;;;5746           {
;;;5747               b SET_TO block->b_number;
;;;5748               parameters[5205 + (p_int * 20)] SET_TO b;
;;;5749           }
;;;5750           else
;;;5751               b SET_TO parameters[5205 + (p_int * 20)];
;;;5752   #endif
;;;5753   
;;;5754   #ifdef CC
;;;5755           if (block->c_flag IS ON)
;;;5756           {
;;;5757               c SET_TO block->c_number;
;;;5758               parameters[5206 + (p_int * 20)] SET_TO c;
;;;5759           }
;;;5760           else
;;;5761               c SET_TO parameters[5206 + (p_int * 20)];
;;;5762   #endif

                          AREA ||i.convert_straight_comp1||, CODE, READONLY, ALIGN=2

                  convert_straight_comp1 PROC
;;;6473   
;;;6474       static int convert_straight_comp1(            /* ARGUMENTS                       */
000000  e92d4fff          PUSH     {r0-r11,lr}
;;;6475       int move,                                     /* either G_0 or G_1                         */
;;;6476       block_pointer block,                          /* pointer to a block of RS274 instructions  */
;;;6477       setup_pointer settings,                       /* pointer to machine settings               */
;;;6478       double px,                                    /* X coordinate of end point                 */
;;;6479       double py,                                    /* Y coordinate of end point                 */
;;;6480       double end_z                                  /* Z coordinate of end point                 */
;;;6481   #ifdef AA
;;;6482       , double AA_end                               /* A coordinate of end point           *//*AA*/

                  convert_straight_comp2 PROC
;;;6663   
;;;6664       static int convert_straight_comp2(            /* ARGUMENTS                       */
000000  e92d4fff          PUSH     {r0-r11,lr}
;;;6665       int move,                                     /* either G_0 or G_1                         */
;;;6666       block_pointer block,                          /* pointer to a block of RS274 instructions  */
;;;6667       setup_pointer settings,                       /* pointer to machine settings               */
;;;6668       double px,                                    /* X coordinate of programmed end point      */
;;;6669       double py,                                    /* Y coordinate of programmed end point      */
;;;6670       double end_z                                  /* Z coordinate of end point                 */
;;;6671   #ifdef AA
;;;6672       , double AA_end                               /* A coordinate of end point           *//*AA*/
;;;6673   #endif
;;;6674   #ifdef BB
;;;6675       , double BB_end                               /* B coordinate of end point           *//*BB*/
;;;6676   #endif
;;;6677   #ifdef CC
;;;6678       , double CC_end                               /* C coordinate of end point           *//*CC*/
;;;6679   #endif
;;;6680       )
;;;6681       {
000004  b0a3              SUB      sp,sp,#0x8c
000006  4692              MOV      r10,r2
000008  e9dd4534          LDRD     r4,r5,[sp,#0xd0]
;;;6682           static char name[] SET_TO "convert_straight_comp2";
;;;6683           double alpha;
;;;6684           double beta;
;;;6685           double end_x;                             /* x-coordinate of actual end point */
;;;6686           double end_y;                             /* y-coordinate of actual end point */
;;;6687           double gamma;
;;;6688           double mid_x;                             /* x-coordinate of end of added arc, if needed */
;;;6689           double mid_y;                             /* y-coordinate of end of added arc, if needed */
;;;6690           double radius;
;;;6691           int side;
;;;6692      /* radians, testing corners */
;;;6693           double small SET_TO TOLERANCE_CONCAVE_CORNER;
00000c  49fe              LDR      r1,|L51.1032|
00000e  48ff              LDR      r0,|L51.1036|
000010  e9cd1014          STRD     r1,r0,[sp,#0x50]
;;;6694           double start_x, start_y;                  /* programmed beginning point */
;;;6695           double theta;
;;;6696   
;;;6697           start_x SET_TO settings->program_x;
000014  f50a4130          ADD      r1,r10,#0xb000
000018  f50171bc          ADD      r1,r1,#0x178
00001c  c903              LDM      r1,{r0,r1}
00001e  e9cd0112          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x48]
;;;6698           start_y SET_TO settings->program_y;
000022  f50a4030          ADD      r0,r10,#0xb000
000026  f50070c0          ADD      r0,r0,#0x180
00002a  c803              LDM      r0,{r0,r1}
00002c  e9cd0110          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x40]
;;;6699           if ((py IS start_y) AND (px IS start_x))  /* no XY motion */

000034  e9dd0132          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0xc8]

00003c  d15c              BNE      |L51.248|
00003e  e9dd2312          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x48]
000042  e9dd0130          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0xc0]
000046  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_cdcmpeq
00004a  d155              BNE      |L51.248|
;;;6700           {
;;;6701               end_x SET_TO settings->current_x;
00004c  f50a7664          ADD      r6,r10,#0x390
000050  cec0              LDM      r6,{r6,r7}
;;;6702               end_y SET_TO settings->current_y;

000056  f8da8398          LDR      r8,[r10,#0x398]
;;;6703               if (move IS G_0)
00005a  9823              LDR      r0,[sp,#0x8c]
00005c  b940              CBNZ     r0,|L51.112|
;;;6704                   STRAIGHT_TRAVERSE(end_x, end_y, end_z
00005e  4642              MOV      r2,r8
000060  464b              MOV      r3,r9

000064  4639              MOV      r1,r7
000066  e9cd4500          STRD     r4,r5,[sp,#0]
00006a  f7fffffe          BL       STRAIGHT_TRAVERSE
00006e  e238              B        |L51.1250|
                  |L51.112|
;;;6705           #ifdef AA
;;;6706                       ,             AA_end
;;;6707           #else
;;;6708           #ifdef ALL_AXES
;;;6709                       , 0
;;;6710           #endif

                          AREA ||i.find_arc_length||, CODE, READONLY, ALIGN=1

                  find_arc_length PROC
;;;7787   
;;;7788       static double find_arc_length(                /* ARGUMENTS                          */
000000  e92d4ff0          PUSH     {r4-r11,lr}
;;;7789       double x1,                                    /* X-coordinate of start point        */
;;;7790       double y1,                                    /* Y-coordinate of start point        */
;;;7791       double z1,                                    /* Z-coordinate of start point        */
;;;7792       double center_x,                              /* X-coordinate of arc center         */
;;;7793       double center_y,                              /* Y-coordinate of arc center         */
;;;7794       int turn,                                     /* no. of full or partial circles CCW */
;;;7795       double x2,                                    /* X-coordinate of end point          */
;;;7796       double y2,                                    /* Y-coordinate of end point          */
;;;7797       double z2)                                    /* Z-coordinate of end point          */
;;;7798       {
000004  b08d              SUB      sp,sp,#0x34
000006  4606              MOV      r6,r0
000008  460f              MOV      r7,r1
00000a  4690              MOV      r8,r2
00000c  4699              MOV      r9,r3
00000e  e9ddab18          LDRD     r10,r11,[sp,#0x60]
;;;7799           double radius;
;;;7800           double theta;                             /* amount of turn of arc in radians */
;;;7801   
;;;7802           radius SET_TO hypot((center_x - x1), (center_y - y1));
000012  4642              MOV      r2,r8
000014  464b              MOV      r3,r9
000016  e9dd011a          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x68]
00001a  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dsub
00001e  4652              MOV      r2,r10
000020  465b              MOV      r3,r11
000022  e9cd0108          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x20]
000026  4630              MOV      r0,r6
000028  4639              MOV      r1,r7
00002a  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_drsub
00002e  e9cd0106          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x18]
000032  e9dd2308          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x20]
000036  f7fffffe          BL       hypot
00003a  e9cd010a          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x28]
;;;7803           theta SET_TO find_turn(x1, y1, center_x, center_y, turn, x2, y2);
00003e  e9dd0120          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x80]
000042  e9cd0108          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x20]
000046  e9dd011e          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x78]
00004a  e9cd0106          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x18]
00004e  981c              LDR      r0,[sp,#0x70]
000050  9004              STR      r0,[sp,#0x10]
000052  e9dd011a          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x68]
000056  4642              MOV      r2,r8
000058  464b              MOV      r3,r9
00005a  e9cdab00          STRD     r10,r11,[sp,#0]
00005e  e9cd0102          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#8]
000062  4630              MOV      r0,r6
000064  4639              MOV      r1,r7
000066  f7fffffe          BL       find_turn
00006a  4604              MOV      r4,r0
00006c  460d              MOV      r5,r1
;;;7804           if (z2 IS z1)
00006e  e9dd2316          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x58]
000072  e9dd0122          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x88]
000076  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_cdcmpeq
00007a  d10b              BNE      |L63.148|
;;;7805               return (radius * fabs(theta));
00007c  f0254000          BIC      r0,r5,#0x80000000
000080  e9cd4008          STRD     r4,r0,[sp,#0x20]
000084  4620              MOV      r0,r4
000086  a909              ADD      r1,sp,#0x24
000088  c90e              LDM      r1,{r1-r3}
00008a  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dmul
                  |L63.142|
;;;7806           else
;;;7807               return hypot((radius * theta), (z2 - z1));
;;;7808       }
00008e  b00d              ADD      sp,sp,#0x34
000090  e8bd8ff0          POP      {r4-r11,pc}
                  |L63.148|
000094  e9dd2316          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x58]      ;7807
000098  e9dd0122          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x88]      ;7807
00009c  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dsub
0000a0  4622              MOV      r2,r4                 ;7807
0000a2  462b              MOV      r3,r5                 ;7807
0000a4  e9cd0108          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x20]      ;7807
0000a8  e9dd010a          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x28]      ;7807
0000ac  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dmul
0000b0  e9cd0106          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x18]      ;7807
0000b4  e9dd2308          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x20]      ;7807
0000b8  f7fffffe          BL       hypot
0000bc  e7e7              B        |L63.142|
;;;7809   
                          ENDP


                          AREA ||i.find_ends||, CODE, READONLY, ALIGN=2

                  find_ends PROC
;;;7849   
;;;7850       static int find_ends(                         /* ARGUMENTS                                    */
000000  e92d4ff0          PUSH     {r4-r11,lr}
;;;7851       block_pointer block,                          /* pointer to a block of RS274/NGC instructions */
;;;7852       setup_pointer settings,                       /* pointer to machine settings                  */
;;;7853       double * px,                                  /* pointer to end_x                             */
;;;7854       double * py,                                  /* pointer to end_y                             */
;;;7855       double * pz                                   /* pointer to end_z                             */
;;;7856   #ifdef AA
;;;7857       , double * AA_p                               /* pointer to end_a                       *//*AA*/
;;;7858   #endif
;;;7859   #ifdef BB
;;;7860       , double * BB_p                               /* pointer to end_b                       *//*BB*/
;;;7861   #endif
;;;7862   #ifdef CC
;;;7863       , double * CC_p                               /* pointer to end_c                       *//*CC*/
;;;7864   #endif
;;;7865       )
;;;7866       {
000004  b087              SUB      sp,sp,#0x1c
000006  4605              MOV      r5,r0
000008  460c              MOV      r4,r1
00000a  4690              MOV      r8,r2
00000c  4699              MOV      r9,r3
00000e  f8dda040          LDR      r10,[sp,#0x40]
;;;7867           int mode;
;;;7868           int middle;
;;;7869           int comp;
;;;7870   
;;;7871           mode SET_TO settings->distance_mode;
000012  f89403f8          LDRB     r0,[r4,#0x3f8]
000016  9006              STR      r0,[sp,#0x18]
;;;7872           middle SET_TO (settings->program_x ISNT UNKNOWN);
000018  f5044130          ADD      r1,r4,#0xb000
00001c  f50171bc          ADD      r1,r1,#0x178
000020  c903              LDM      r1,{r0,r1}
000022  4683              MOV      r11,r0
000024  4aaf              LDR      r2,|L64.740|
000026  4bb0              LDR      r3,|L64.744|
000028  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_cdcmpeq
00002c  d002              BEQ      |L64.52|
00002e  f04f0001          MOV      r0,#1
000032  e001              B        |L64.56|
                  |L64.52|
000034  f04f0000          MOV      r0,#0
                  |L64.56|
000038  4606              MOV      r6,r0
;;;7873           comp SET_TO (settings->cutter_comp_side ISNT OFF);
00003a  f8d403b0          LDR      r0,[r4,#0x3b0]
00003e  b110              CBZ      r0,|L64.70|
000040  f04f0001          MOV      r0,#1
000044  e001              B        |L64.74|
                  |L64.70|
000046  f04f0000          MOV      r0,#0
                  |L64.74|
00004a  4607              MOV      r7,r0
;;;7874   
;;;7875           if (block->g_modes[0] IS G_53)            /* distance mode is absolute in this case */
00004c  f8d50110          LDR      r0,[r5,#0x110]
000050  f5a07100          SUB      r1,r0,#0x200
000054  3912              SUBS     r1,r1,#0x12
000056  d17a              BNE      |L64.334|
;;;7876           {
;;;7877   #ifdef DEBUG_EMC
;;;7878               COMMENT("interpreter: offsets temporarily suspended");
000058  a0a4              ADR      r0,|L64.748|
00005a  f7fffffe          BL       COMMENT
;;;7879   #endif
;;;7880               *px SET_TO (block->x_flag IS ON) ? (block->x_number -
00005e  f8d501dc          LDR      r0,[r5,#0x1dc]
000062  2801              CMP      r0,#1
000064  d11a              BNE      |L64.156|
000066  e9d4011a          LDRD     r0,r1,[r4,#0x68]
00006a  4683              MOV      r11,r0
00006c  468c              MOV      r12,r1
00006e  f50460c6          ADD      r0,r4,#0x630
000072  c803              LDM      r0,{r0,r1}
000074  465a              MOV      r2,r11
000076  4663              MOV      r3,r12
000078  e9cd0102          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#8]
00007c  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dadd
000080  e9cd0104          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x10]
000084  f8d511e0          LDR      r1,[r5,#0x1e0]
000088  468b              MOV      r11,r1
00008a  465a              MOV      r2,r11
00008c  f8d501e4          LDR      r0,[r5,#0x1e4]
000090  4603              MOV      r3,r0
000092  e9dd0104          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x10]
000096  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_drsub
00009a  e002              B        |L64.162|
                  |L64.156|
;;;7881                   (settings->origin_offset_x + settings->axis_offset_x)) :
;;;7882               settings->current_x;
00009c  f5047064          ADD      r0,r4,#0x390
0000a0  c803              LDM      r0,{r0,r1}
                  |L64.162|
0000a2  e9c80100          STRD     r0,r1,[r8,#0]
;;;7883               *py SET_TO (block->y_flag IS ON) ? (block->y_number -
0000a6  f8d501e8          LDR      r0,[r5,#0x1e8]
0000aa  2801              CMP      r0,#1
0000ac  d11d              BNE      |L64.234|
0000ae  e9d4011c          LDRD     r0,r1,[r4,#0x70]
0000b2  e9cd0102          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#8]
0000b6  f8d41638          LDR      r1,[r4,#0x638]
0000ba  468b              MOV      r11,r1
0000bc  f8d4063c          LDR      r0,[r4,#0x63c]
0000c0  4684              MOV      r12,r0
0000c2  4658              MOV      r0,r11
0000c4  4661              MOV      r1,r12
0000c6  e9dd2302          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#8]
0000ca  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dadd
0000ce  e9cd0104          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x10]
0000d2  f8d511f0          LDR      r1,[r5,#0x1f0]
0000d6  468b              MOV      r11,r1
0000d8  465a              MOV      r2,r11
0000da  f8d501f4          LDR      r0,[r5,#0x1f4]
0000de  4603              MOV      r3,r0
0000e0  e9dd0104          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x10]
0000e4  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_drsub
0000e8  e002              B        |L64.240|
                  |L64.234|
;;;7884                   (settings->origin_offset_y + settings->axis_offset_y)) :

                  find_straight_length PROC
;;;8108   
;;;8109       static double find_straight_length(           /* ARGUMENTS   */
000000  e92d4ff0          PUSH     {r4-r11,lr}
;;;8110       double x2,                                    /* X-coordinate of end point    */
;;;8111       double y2,                                    /* Y-coordinate of end point    */
;;;8112       double z2,                                    /* Z-coordinate of end point    */
;;;8113   #ifdef AA
;;;8114       double AA_2,      /* A-coordinate of end point    */ /*AA*/
;;;8115   #endif
;;;8116   #ifdef BB
;;;8117       double BB_2,      /* B-coordinate of end point    */ /*BB*/
;;;8118   #endif
;;;8119   #ifdef CC
;;;8120       double CC_2,      /* C-coordinate of end point    */ /*CC*/
;;;8121   #endif
;;;8122       double x1,                                    /* X-coordinate of start point  */
;;;8123       double y1,                                    /* Y-coordinate of start point  */
;;;8124       double z1                                     /* Z-coordinate of start point  */
;;;8125   #ifdef AA
;;;8126       , double AA_1     /* A-coordinate of start point  */ /*AA*/
;;;8127   #endif
;;;8128   #ifdef BB
;;;8129       , double BB_1     /* B-coordinate of start point  */ /*BB*/
;;;8130   #endif
;;;8131   #ifdef CC
;;;8132       , double CC_1     /* C-coordinate of start point  */ /*CC*/
;;;8133   #endif
;;;8134       )
;;;8135       {
000004  b08d              SUB      sp,sp,#0x34
000006  4604              MOV      r4,r0
000008  460d              MOV      r5,r1
00000a  4616              MOV      r6,r2
00000c  461f              MOV      r7,r3
00000e  e9ddab18          LDRD     r10,r11,[sp,#0x60]
000012  e9dd8916          LDRD     r8,r9,[sp,#0x58]
;;;8136           if ((x1 ISNT x2) OR (y1 ISNT y2) OR (z1 ISNT z2) OR
000016  4652              MOV      r2,r10
000018  465b              MOV      r3,r11
00001a  4620              MOV      r0,r4
00001c  4629              MOV      r1,r5
00001e  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_cdcmpeq
000022  d10e              BNE      |L66.66|
000024  4632              MOV      r2,r6
000026  463b              MOV      r3,r7
000028  e9dd011a          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x68]
00002c  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_cdcmpeq
000030  d107              BNE      |L66.66|
000032  4642              MOV      r2,r8
000034  464b              MOV      r3,r9
000036  e9dd011c          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x70]
00003a  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_cdcmpeq
00003e  d100              BNE      |L66.66|
;;;8137               (1
000040  bf00              NOP      
                  |L66.66|
;;;8138       #ifdef AA
;;;8139               AND (AA_2 IS AA_1)                    /*AA*/
;;;8140       #endif
;;;8141       #ifdef BB
;;;8142               AND (BB_2 IS BB_1)                    /*BB*/
;;;8143       #endif
;;;8144       #ifdef CC
;;;8145               AND (CC_2 IS CC_1)                    /*CC*/
;;;8146       #endif
;;;8147               ))                                    /* straight line */
;;;8148               return sqrt(pow((x2 - x1),2) + pow((y2 - y1),2) + pow((z2 - z1),2));
000042  4640              MOV      r0,r8
000044  4649              MOV      r1,r9
000046  e9dd231c          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x70]
00004a  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dsub
00004e  2200              MOVS     r2,#0
000050  f04f4380          MOV      r3,#0x40000000
000054  e9cd0104          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x10]
000058  f7fffffe          BL       pow
00005c  e9cd0108          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x20]
000060  4630              MOV      r0,r6
000062  4639              MOV      r1,r7
000064  e9dd231a          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x68]
000068  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dsub
00006c  2200              MOVS     r2,#0
00006e  f04f4380          MOV      r3,#0x40000000
000072  e9cd0100          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0]
000076  f7fffffe          BL       pow
00007a  4652              MOV      r2,r10
00007c  465b              MOV      r3,r11
00007e  e9cd0104          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x10]
000082  4620              MOV      r0,r4
000084  4629              MOV      r1,r5
000086  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dsub
00008a  2200              MOVS     r2,#0
00008c  f04f4380          MOV      r3,#0x40000000
000090  e9cd0100          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0]
000094  f7fffffe          BL       pow
000098  e9cd0102          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#8]
00009c  e9dd2304          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x10]
0000a0  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dadd
0000a4  e9cd0106          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x18]
0000a8  e9dd2308          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x20]
0000ac  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dadd
0000b0  e9cd010a          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x28]
0000b4  f7fffffe          BL       sqrt
;;;8149           else
;;;8150               return sqrt(0 +
;;;8151           #ifdef AA
;;;8152                   pow((AA_2 - AA_1), 2) +           /*AA*/
;;;8153           #endif
;;;8154           #ifdef BB
;;;8155                   pow((BB_2 - BB_1), 2) +           /*BB*/
;;;8156           #endif
;;;8157           #ifdef CC
;;;8158                   pow((CC_2 - CC_1), 2) +           /*CC*/
;;;8159           #endif
;;;8160                   0);
;;;8161       }
0000b8  b00d              ADD      sp,sp,#0x34
0000ba  e8bd8ff0          POP      {r4-r11,pc}
;;;8162   
                          ENDP


                          AREA ||i.find_turn||, CODE, READONLY, ALIGN=2

                  find_turn PROC
;;;8176   
;;;8177       static double find_turn(                      /* ARGUMENTS                          */
000000  e92d47ff          PUSH     {r0-r10,lr}
;;;8178       double x1,                                    /* X-coordinate of start point        */
;;;8179       double y1,                                    /* Y-coordinate of start point        */
;;;8180       double center_x,                              /* X-coordinate of arc center         */
;;;8181       double center_y,                              /* Y-coordinate of arc center         */
;;;8182       int turn,                                     /* no. of full or partial circles CCW */
;;;8183       double x2,                                    /* X-coordinate of end point          */
;;;8184       double y2)                                    /* Y-coordinate of end point          */
;;;8185       {
000004  b086              SUB      sp,sp,#0x18
000006  f8dda058          LDR      r10,[sp,#0x58]
;;;8186           double alpha;                             /* angle of first radius                      */
;;;8187           double beta;                              /* angle of second radius                     */
;;;8188           double theta;                             /* amount of turn of arc CCW - negative if CW */
;;;8189   
;;;8190           if (turn IS 0)
00000a  f1ba0f00          CMP      r10,#0
00000e  d104              BNE      |L67.26|
;;;8191               return 0.0;
000010  2000              MOVS     r0,#0
000012  4601              MOV      r1,r0
                  |L67.20|
;;;8192           alpha SET_TO atan2((y1 - center_y), (x1 - center_x));
;;;8193           beta SET_TO atan2((y2 - center_y), (x2 - center_x));
;;;8194           if (turn > 0)
;;;8195           {
;;;8196               if (beta <= alpha)
;;;8197                   beta SET_TO (beta + TWO_PI);
;;;8198               theta SET_TO ((beta - alpha) + ((turn - 1) * TWO_PI));
;;;8199           }
;;;8200           else                                      /* turn < 0 */
;;;8201           {
;;;8202               if (alpha <= beta)
;;;8203                   alpha SET_TO (alpha + TWO_PI);
;;;8204               theta SET_TO ((beta - alpha) + ((turn + 1) * TWO_PI));
;;;8205           }
;;;8206           return (theta);
;;;8207       }
000014  b00a              ADD      sp,sp,#0x28
000016  e8bd87f0          POP      {r4-r10,pc}
                  |L67.26|
00001a  e9dd2312          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x48]      ;8192
00001e  e9dd0106          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x18]      ;8192
000022  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dsub
000026  e9cd0104          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x10]      ;8192
00002a  e9dd2314          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x50]      ;8192
00002e  e9dd0108          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x20]      ;8192
000032  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dsub
000036  e9cd0102          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#8]         ;8192
00003a  e9dd2304          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x10]      ;8192
00003e  f7fffffe          BL       atan2
000042  4606              MOV      r6,r0                 ;8192
000044  460f              MOV      r7,r1                 ;8192
000046  e9dd2312          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x48]      ;8193
00004a  e9dd0118          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x60]      ;8193
00004e  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dsub
000052  e9cd0104          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x10]      ;8193
000056  e9dd2314          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x50]      ;8193
00005a  e9dd011a          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x68]      ;8193
00005e  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dsub
000062  e9cd0102          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#8]         ;8193
000066  e9dd2304          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x10]      ;8193
00006a  f7fffffe          BL       atan2
00006e  4604              MOV      r4,r0                 ;8193
000070  460d              MOV      r5,r1                 ;8193
000072  f1ba0f00          CMP      r10,#0                ;8194
000076  dd2a              BLE      |L67.206|

000080  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_cdcmple
000084  d807              BHI      |L67.150|
000086  4a28              LDR      r2,|L67.296|
000088  4b28              LDR      r3,|L67.300|
00008a  4620              MOV      r0,r4                 ;8197
00008c  4629              MOV      r1,r5                 ;8197
00008e  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dadd
000092  4604              MOV      r4,r0                 ;8197

                  init_block PROC
;;;8246   
;;;8247       static int init_block(                        /* ARGUMENTS                                     */
000000  4601              MOV      r1,r0

;;;8249       {

;;;8254   #ifdef BB

00001a  f8c1010c          STR      r0,[r1,#0x10c]
;;;8263           for (n SET_TO 0; n < 14; n++)

000024  e008              B        |L68.56|
                  |L68.38|
;;;8264           {
;;;8265               block->g_modes[n] SET_TO -1;

00003a  dbf4              BLT      |L68.38|
;;;8266           }
;;;8267           block->h_number SET_TO -1;

000040  f50171a4          ADD      r1,r1,#0x148
000044  6008              STR      r0,[r1,#0]
;;;8268           block->i_flag SET_TO OFF;

00004a  6048              STR      r0,[r1,#4]
;;;8269           block->j_flag SET_TO OFF;

;;;8270           block->k_flag SET_TO OFF;

;;;8271           block->l_number SET_TO -1;

;;;8272           block->line_number SET_TO -1;

;;;8273           block->motion_to_be SET_TO -1;

;;;8274           block->m_count SET_TO 0;
00005a  f04f0000          MOV      r0,#0
00005e  63c8              STR      r0,[r1,#0x3c]

;;;8275           for (n SET_TO 0; n < 10; n++)
000064  4602              MOV      r2,r0
000066  e008              B        |L68.122|
                  |L68.104|
;;;8276           {
;;;8277               block->m_modes[n] SET_TO -1;
000068  f04f33ff          MOV      r3,#0xffffffff

000070  f8403022          STR      r3,[r0,r2,LSL #2]

                  |L68.122|
00007a  2a0a              CMP      r2,#0xa               ;8275
00007c  dbf4              BLT      |L68.104|
;;;8278           }
;;;8279           block->p_number SET_TO -1.0;

;;;8280           block->q_number SET_TO -1.0;

                          AREA ||i.inverse_time_rate_arc||, CODE, READONLY, ALIGN=2

                  inverse_time_rate_arc PROC
;;;8309   
;;;8310       static int inverse_time_rate_arc(             /* ARGUMENTS                       */
000000  e92d4ff0          PUSH     {r4-r11,lr}
;;;8311       double x1,                                    /* x coord of start point of arc            */
;;;8312       double y1,                                    /* y coord of start point of arc            */
;;;8313       double z1,                                    /* z coord of start point of arc            */
;;;8314       double cx,                                    /* x coord of center of arc                 */
;;;8315       double cy,                                    /* y coord of center of arc                 */
;;;8316       int turn,                                     /* turn of arc                              */
;;;8317       double x2,                                    /* x coord of end point of arc              */
;;;8318       double y2,                                    /* y coord of end point of arc              */
;;;8319       double z2,                                    /* z coord of end point of arc              */
;;;8320       block_pointer block,                          /* pointer to a block of RS274 instructions */
;;;8321       setup_pointer settings)                       /* pointer to machine settings              */
;;;8322       {
000004  b091              SUB      sp,sp,#0x44
000006  4606              MOV      r6,r0
000008  460f              MOV      r7,r1

00000c  4699              MOV      r9,r3

;;;8323           double length;
;;;8324           double rate;
;;;8325   
;;;8326           length SET_TO find_arc_length (x1, y1, z1, cx, cy, turn, x2, y2, z2);

00001a  e9dd0124          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x90]
00001e  e9cd010a          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x28]
000022  e9dd0122          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x88]
000026  e9cd0108          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x20]
00002a  9820              LDR      r0,[sp,#0x80]

000032  e9cd0104          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x10]
000036  e9dd011c          LDRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x70]
00003a  4642              MOV      r2,r8
00003c  464b              MOV      r3,r9
00003e  e9cdab00          STRD     r10,r11,[sp,#0]
000042  e9cd0102          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#8]
000046  4630              MOV      r0,r6
000048  4639              MOV      r1,r7
00004a  f7fffffe          BL       find_arc_length
00004e  e9cd010e          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x38]
;;;8327           rate SET_TO MAX(0.1, (length * block->f_number));
000052  9828              LDR      r0,[sp,#0xa0]
000054  f5007084          ADD      r0,r0,#0x108
000058  c803              LDM      r0,{r0,r1}
00005a  e9cd010a          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x28]
00005e  e9dd230e          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x38]
000062  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dmul
000066  4a11              LDR      r2,|L69.172|
000068  4b11              LDR      r3,|L69.176|
00006a  e9cd010c          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x30]
00006e  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_cdcmple
000072  d202              BCS      |L69.122|
000074  480d              LDR      r0,|L69.172|
000076  490e              LDR      r1,|L69.176|
000078  e009              B        |L69.142|
                  |L69.122|
00007a  9928              LDR      r1,[sp,#0xa0]
00007c  f5017184          ADD      r1,r1,#0x108
000080  c903              LDM      r1,{r0,r1}
000082  e9cd010c          STRD     r0,r1,[sp,#0x30]
000086  e9dd230e          LDRD     r2,r3,[sp,#0x38]
00008a  f7fffffe          BL       __aeabi_dmul
                  |L69.142|

                  parse_line PROC
;;;8563   
;;;8564       static int parse_line(                        /* ARGUMENTS                            */
000000  e92d41f0          PUSH     {r4-r8,lr}

;;;8566       block_pointer block,                          /* pointer to a block to be filled      */

;;;8568       {
000004  4605              MOV      r5,r0
000006  460e              MOV      r6,r1
000008  4614              MOV      r4,r2
;;;8569           static char name[] SET_TO "parse_line";

;;;8571   
;;;8572           CHP(init_block (block));

00005a  4638              MOV      r0,r7
                  |L73.92|
